<item>
            <title>[LU-3118] sanity-lfsck test_6a: Expect larger than: 13, but got 13 </title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3118</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Andreas Dilger &amp;lt;andreas.dilger@intel.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/66a9f45e-9965-11e2-adf7-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/66a9f45e-9965-11e2-adf7-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt; for the &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3039&quot; title=&quot;OI scrub and LFSCK do not work on lustre-2.4&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-3039&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-3039&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; patch, which was just landed to master.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_6a failed with the following error in the test logs:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;(7) Expect larger than: 13, but got 13&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It appears that this relates to restart of the scrub after MDS restart.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Info required for matching: sanity-lfsck 6a&lt;/p&gt;</description>
